Class Resource

  • java.lang.Object
    • resource.Resource

  • public class Resource
extends java.lang.Object
    main function is performing different algorithms on delivered processes: RR - round robin, SJF - shortest job first, FCFS- first come first served uses build Timer class to measure data for analysis
